   167|   167|                        <h2 class="font-heading text-brand-green font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-xs sm:text-sm mb-2">About Us</h2>
   168|   168|                        <h3 class="font-heading text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-dark mb-4 sm:mb-6">Expert Guttering from Colne to Skipton</h3>
   169|   169|                        
   170|   170|                        <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4 text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-lg">
   171|   171|                            <p>
   172|   172|                                Based at Pine Garth Farm in Colne, <strong class="text-brand-dark font-semibold">Lancashire Aluminium Seamless Guttering</strong> provides top-tier roofline solutions across the region. We pride ourselves on delivering a flawless finish that protects your home from the UK weather.
   173|   173|                            </p>
   174|   174|                            <p>
   175|   175|                                Traditional plastic gutters are joined together, and over time, those seals perish and leak. Our system is different. We bring our forming machine directly to your property and create a single, continuous gutter measured exactly to your roofline. 
   176|   176|                            </p>
